{
    "publish_date": "2013-01-15T20:00:47.000Z", 
    "video_length": "PT7M10S", 
    "captions": [
        {
            "text": "My name is Christian\nvon Koenigsegg.", 
            "dur": "1.795", 
            "start": "0.386"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I&#39;m 40 years old.", 
            "dur": "1.285", 
            "start": "2.181"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And for half of my life I&#39;ve\nbeen on the quest to be a", 
            "dur": "2.14", 
            "start": "3.466"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "leader in the hypercar industry,\nutilizing Swedish", 
            "dur": "3.28", 
            "start": "5.606"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "design combined with visionary\ntechnical solutions.", 
            "dur": "2.7", 
            "start": "8.886"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Our latest car, the Agera R, is\nbuilt in the old hangars of", 
            "dur": "3.8", 
            "start": "15.256"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "a former Swedish fighter\njet&#39;s squadron.", 
            "dur": "2.28", 
            "start": "19.056"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Their symbol, a ghost, is now\nproudly painted on the back of", 
            "dur": "4.06", 
            "start": "21.336"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "every Koenigsegg.", 
            "dur": "1.25", 
            "start": "25.396"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "[CAR ENGINE]", 
            "dur": "25.314", 
            "start": "29.002"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So here we are at station\nsix out of seven in", 
            "dur": "3.285", 
            "start": "54.316"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "our production line.", 
            "dur": "1.175", 
            "start": "57.601"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And I&#39;m going to talk a little\nbit about our rear suspension", 
            "dur": "3.05", 
            "start": "58.776"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "on the car.", 
            "dur": "0.91", 
            "start": "61.826"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "If you want a car to go fast,\nand especially around a track", 
            "dur": "2.84", 
            "start": "62.736"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and in cornering and braking and\nall of these aspects, it&#39;s", 
            "dur": "2.41", 
            "start": "65.576"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "not enough with a\npowerful engine.", 
            "dur": "1.53", 
            "start": "67.986"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "You also need a chassis and a\nsuspension which is up to", 
            "dur": "3.94", 
            "start": "69.516"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "snuff to get the power to\nthe ground, really.", 
            "dur": "4.38", 
            "start": "73.456"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So here we-- when I open this,\nyou can see what we call the", 
            "dur": "3.64", 
            "start": "77.836"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Triplex suspension.", 
            "dur": "1.38", 
            "start": "81.476"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "First of all, it&#39;s\nvery unique.", 
            "dur": "1.02", 
            "start": "82.856"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And it really enables our car\nto get maximum traction,", 
            "dur": "4.21", 
            "start": "83.876"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "maximum level of comfort.", 
            "dur": "1.36", 
            "start": "88.086"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "This is actually a\nroad car as well.", 
            "dur": "2.84", 
            "start": "89.446"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "But with very little compromise\nbetween comfort and", 
            "dur": "3.236", 
            "start": "92.286"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "handling and stability.", 
            "dur": "3.984", 
            "start": "95.522"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "[CAR ENGINE]", 
            "dur": "10.5", 
            "start": "99.506"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "It&#39;s basically one extra shock\nabsorber connecting the rear", 
            "dur": "6.24", 
            "start": "110.006"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "wheels together.", 
            "dur": "0.76", 
            "start": "116.246"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "They have one shock absorber\neach here going down into the", 
            "dur": "3.29", 
            "start": "117.006"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "chassis with the spring\nholding the car up.", 
            "dur": "2.69", 
            "start": "120.296"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "But then there is this extra\nshock absorber tying the", 
            "dur": "3.07", 
            "start": "122.986"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "wheels together.", 
            "dur": "1.08", 
            "start": "126.056"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And underneath here you can see\nour quite unique z-shaped", 
            "dur": "3.03", 
            "start": "127.136"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "anti-roll bar.", 
            "dur": "1.52", 
            "start": "130.166"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So the reason why we developed\nthis third damper connecting", 
            "dur": "4.27", 
            "start": "131.686"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "the sides together is that we\nwere getting so much power in", 
            "dur": "2.93", 
            "start": "135.956"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "the car that we were getting\nmore and more squat during", 
            "dur": "3.12", 
            "start": "138.886"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "take-off, which in one way\nis good, to get traction.", 
            "dur": "4.23", 
            "start": "142.006"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "But you don&#39;t want too much\nmovement in the car so it&#39;s", 
            "dur": "2.59", 
            "start": "146.236"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "easy to handle and\nthat it&#39;s stable.", 
            "dur": "1.71", 
            "start": "148.826"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "But you still want a lot\nof traction, of course.", 
            "dur": "2.758", 
            "start": "150.536"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "[CAR ENGINE]", 
            "dur": "13.642", 
            "start": "153.294"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Most manufacturers solved this\nneed by changing the geometry", 
            "dur": "6.14", 
            "start": "166.936"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "of the suspension so the car\ncan&#39;t squat due to geometric", 
            "dur": "4.39", 
            "start": "173.076"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "restriction.", 
            "dur": "1.14", 
            "start": "177.466"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "The backside of doing that is\nthat it dilutes the geometry", 
            "dur": "5.74", 
            "start": "178.606"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "that you need for cornering\nand the", 
            "dur": "1.71", 
            "start": "184.346"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "other parts of handling.", 
            "dur": "2.13", 
            "start": "186.056"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "In a way, it&#39;s an anti-squat\ndamper.", 
            "dur": "2.02", 
            "start": "188.186"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "It means we can have\na truer suspension", 
            "dur": "3", 
            "start": "190.206"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "geometry than otherwise.", 
            "dur": "1.96", 
            "start": "193.206"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "On top of that, it has other\nside effects, as it is a new", 
            "dur": "5.1", 
            "start": "195.166"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "dimension of dampening where you\nhave forces going from one", 
            "dur": "3.13", 
            "start": "200.266"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "wheel to the other.", 
            "dur": "1.91", 
            "start": "203.396"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So for example, if you&#39;re\ndriving on a road which is a", 
            "dur": "2.82", 
            "start": "205.306"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "little bit uneven from left to\nright hand side, you have", 
            "dur": "4.02", 
            "start": "208.126"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "independent movement of the\nwheels, which is good.", 
            "dur": "2.69", 
            "start": "212.146"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "But then you have the anti-roll\nbar, which is there", 
            "dur": "2.4", 
            "start": "214.836"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "to stabilize in cornering, which\nyou&#39;d rather not even", 
            "dur": "2.82", 
            "start": "217.236"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "have while driving straight on\na bumpy road, as it makes the", 
            "dur": "3.3", 
            "start": "220.056"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "car feel a little bit less\ncomfortable than without it.", 
            "dur": "3.42", 
            "start": "223.356"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "But what&#39;s interesting is that\nthis damper actually", 
            "dur": "2.79", 
            "start": "226.776"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "counteracts the forces of the", 
            "dur": "2.3", 
            "start": "229.566"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "anti-roll bar in that situation.", 
            "dur": "1.52", 
            "start": "231.866"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So when this wheel moves up on\na bump and this is not hit by", 
            "dur": "3.675", 
            "start": "233.386"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "a bump, but you&#39;re still driving\nstraight, this link", 
            "dur": "3.595", 
            "start": "237.061"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "here pushes the anti-roll bar\nthis direction, pulls a", 
            "dur": "3.17", 
            "start": "240.656"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "similar link on this side that\ndirection, and wants to lift", 
            "dur": "2.9", 
            "start": "243.826"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "this wheel up as well, which\ncauses on all cars with", 
            "dur": "2.88", 
            "start": "246.726"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "anti-roll bars a certain\namount of harshness.", 
            "dur": "5.16", 
            "start": "249.606"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "But when that is happening when\ndriving straight on a", 
            "dur": "3.152", 
            "start": "254.766"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "road like that, this shock\nabsorber actually sends the", 
            "dur": "3.158", 
            "start": "257.918"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "force to this side of the wheel,\ncounteracting the force", 
            "dur": "3.02", 
            "start": "261.076"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "of the anti-roll bar, cancelling\nthat energy out.", 
            "dur": "2.81", 
            "start": "264.096"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So you get the same or similar\ntype of comfort in a straight", 
            "dur": "3.64", 
            "start": "266.906"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "line as if you did not have an\nanti-roll bar, which is a", 
            "dur": "3.4", 
            "start": "270.546"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "great side effect.", 
            "dur": "1.64", 
            "start": "273.946"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "[CAR ENGINE]", 
            "dur": "7.71", 
            "start": "275.586"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Also, the damping curves of this\nshock absorber are very,", 
            "dur": "4.25", 
            "start": "283.296"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "very special.", 
            "dur": "1.06", 
            "start": "287.546"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Basically it&#39;s focusing on\nlow-speed damping force.", 
            "dur": "4.2", 
            "start": "288.606"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So when you get high speed, when\nyou hit something harsh", 
            "dur": "2.89", 
            "start": "292.806"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and fast, basically it&#39;s\nnot doing much.", 
            "dur": "4.11", 
            "start": "295.696"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "It&#39;s more for the lower-speed", 
            "dur": "2.11", 
            "start": "299.806"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "dampening, where it&#39;s efficient.", 
            "dur": "1.62", 
            "start": "301.916"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So there are a lot of different\nphilosophies that", 
            "dur": "2.41", 
            "start": "303.536"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "can be applied and that we can\nenhance in the future.", 
            "dur": "3.71", 
            "start": "305.946"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "But the starting point is to\nreduce squat, increase", 
            "dur": "3.52", 
            "start": "309.656"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "comfort, and reduce roll by the\nfact that we can have a", 
            "dur": "3.2", 
            "start": "313.176"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "stiffer anti-roll bar than\nwe otherwise could", 
            "dur": "2.83", 
            "start": "316.376"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "have without it.", 
            "dur": "1.325", 
            "start": "319.206"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "[CAR ENGINE]", 
            "dur": "6.045", 
            "start": "320.531"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Now at the front of the car, we\ncan see we have a similarly", 
            "dur": "3.48", 
            "start": "326.576"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "complex suspension layout.", 
            "dur": "2.62", 
            "start": "330.056"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And actually here, everything\nis very, very low, to have,", 
            "dur": "3.46", 
            "start": "332.676"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "again, as low center of\ngravity as possible.", 
            "dur": "3.27", 
            "start": "336.136"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "But also we needed to make it\nlow to be able to get our roof", 
            "dur": "3.15", 
            "start": "339.406"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "into the car, which is a\nvery unique feature.", 
            "dur": "2.8", 
            "start": "342.556"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So we couldn&#39;t have anything\nin the way for the roof to", 
            "dur": "2.48", 
            "start": "345.356"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "slide in here.", 
            "dur": "1.96", 
            "start": "347.836"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "But it had the side effect of\nactually also lowering the", 
            "dur": "2.6", 
            "start": "349.796"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "center of gravity.", 
            "dur": "0.87", 
            "start": "352.396"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So that&#39;s a perfect example of\ntwo needs working together", 
            "dur": "5.08", 
            "start": "353.266"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "without compromise.", 
            "dur": "0.77", 
            "start": "358.346"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "[CAR ENGINE]", 
            "dur": "9.39", 
            "start": "359.116"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Extreme [INAUDIBLE] technology,\nextreme brake", 
            "dur": "3.82", 
            "start": "368.506"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "technology, all of these systems\ncombined made it", 
            "dur": "6.04", 
            "start": "372.326"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "possible for us to take the\nworld record from 0 to 300 to", 
            "dur": "5.925", 
            "start": "378.366"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "0 kilometers per hour.", 
            "dur": "1.705", 
            "start": "384.291"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "It&#39;s really all the systems\nworking together.", 
            "dur": "2.08", 
            "start": "385.996"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "If one of the systems, like\nsuspension or brakes or engine", 
            "dur": "3.34", 
            "start": "388.076"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "or gearbox, weren&#39;t up to the\ntask, we could not make a", 
            "dur": "3.405", 
            "start": "391.416"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "record like that.", 
            "dur": "1.135", 
            "start": "394.821"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So it&#39;s all systems working\ntogether, putting the power to", 
            "dur": "3.67", 
            "start": "395.956"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "the ground, creating stability,\ncreating traction", 
            "dur": "3.56", 
            "start": "399.626"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and braking power.", 
            "dur": "1.04", 
            "start": "403.186"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "[MUSIC PLAYING]", 
            "dur": "21.992", 
            "start": "404.226"
        }
    ], 
